            • Test_D:  m_3/m_2 = cos(π/30)/cos(π/5) ≈ 1.229.  No clean
                       framework match.  Test FAILS.

  PART 6.  STRUCTURAL TEST — J₄ DENOMINATOR ↔ E₈ COXETER NUMBER.
            • h(E₈) = 30 = J₄ irrational eigenvalue denominator.
              [Re-stated from MagicSquareUnification.]
            • J₄ eigenvalues: λ₁ = 3/5 and (5±√7)/30 — denominator 30,
              numerator carrier 5±√7 with N_total in numerator and
