    PART 10: HONEST VERDICT TAG
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ -/

/-- **VERDICT TAG: OEIS finding GENUINE; Zamolodchikov-mass match
    NOT SUPPORTED.**

    The OEIS observation that the E₈ exponents are (ℤ/30)*, with
    30 = N_W · N_c · N_total atomic, is a CLEAN structural
